      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BROOKDENE (1) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a nose (26.16) behind Alveston at this track. The form from her last run stacks up well. Expected to feature in the finish again. LOCHINVAR HORNET (3) boasts a strong record this course with two wins and two minors from six tries. In the money last time at this track (26.34) in a Grade 5, finishing a 0.8 lengths third. Looks well placed here and among the chances. HEARTBREAK KID (4) was in the minors two back (16.29) at Launceston but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Cannot be taken lightly. INNER VISION (2) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
